data.lean: lemma succ_mul (a b : mynat) : succ a * b = a * b + b :=

induction b with b h,
  rw [
    mul_zero (succ a),
    mul_zero a,
    zero_add 0

  refl,

  rw [
    mul_succ (succ a) b,
    add_succ (succ a * b) a,
    add_succ (a * succ b) b,
    succ_eq_add_one b,
    mul_add a b 1,
    mul_one a,
    add_right_comm (a * b) a b,

  refl,

data.lean: lemma add_mul (a b t : mynat) : (a + b) * t = a * t + b * t :=

induction a with a h,
  rw [
    zero_mul t,
    zero_add b,
    zero_add (b * t)
  ],
  refl,

  rw [
    succ_add a b,
    succ_mul (a + b) t,
    succ_mul a t,
    add_right_comm (a * t) t (b * t),
    h
  ],
  refl,
